      <p class="text-xl text-[var(--text-secondary)] mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Master the foundation of modern wealth building. Learn how Exchange-Traded Funds work, how to evaluate them, and how to construct a resilient portfolio designed for long-term compounding.</p>

